                                                    1.21748524750428
    0.53152773638616       2   -2.20252209128652    0.73493500080287
                                                   -1.67875577707861
    &END 
    CONFINEMENT_TYPE  BARRIER
    CONFINEMENT 200. 4.0 12.0
  &END POTENTIAL

  &POWELL
     ACCURACY   1.e-14
     STEP_SIZE  0.0025
     MAX_INIT   25
     MAX_FUN    200
     STEP_SIZE_SCALING  0.925
     WEIGHT_PSIR0 0.0
